  statement.  One of the four founding members to bring OpenStack inside the
  walls of AT&T.

  I was responsible for scaling and operationalizing disperse OpenStack
  components over many iterations, into a stable production ready internal
  utility cloud.  Architected and developed data center automation. Provisioned
