  DNS, by parsing standardized ODM/OEM hardware manifests.  Setup Gerrit so our
  team can follow the same workflow for internal projects/repos as OpenStack.
  Led a team of engineers to accomplish the aforementioned through Pivotal
  stories, and interaction through IRC/Google hangouts.

  The ATT OpenStack Chef cookbooks became the de facto community cookbooks used
  to deploy OpenStack. The cookbooks are available on the stackforge's Github
